0.text: Bug 25999  [Import/Export] Importing a second project with a name whose first few characters are similar to an existing one.

1.text: hi, I have a project called "XYZ" in my workbench.

2.text: I used to have another project  with the name "XYZ_plugin" which I had deleted from the workbench some time  ago.

3.text: I found that I needed to refer to some classes on this XYZ_plugin project  and tried to use the File > Import wizard.

4.text: In the text box where I needed to  point to the file-system location, as I typed XYZ_, the project name still  showed up as "XYZ" and so I got an error saying that there was already a  project existing with that name.

5.text: Finally I had to create a new project and  point it at the location.

6.text: But I think this is a bug.
